name: Dream Loving Fellas XIIII
description:
The cat is mystical, magical, psychic and at the same time earthly, guardian of the here and now (Hic et nunc), but also of tomorrow and yesterday that occur, at the same time, in the present. They are great protectors, balancers and transmuters of energy. They see and perceive things that we humans don't understand.

Dambass 2021
